(a_n)
\alpha,\beta>0
2\alpha/\beta
a_n=\alpha+\beta n,\quad\alpha\,,\beta>0
\begin{align} \big(\frac{a_1+a_{n+1}}{a_n}\big)^n&=\exp\big(n\ln(\frac{2\alpha+\beta(n+1)}{\beta n})\big)\\ &=\exp\big(n\ln(1+\frac{2\alpha+\beta}{\beta n})\big)\\ &\leq\exp\big(n\frac{2\alpha+\beta}{\beta n}\big)\\ &\leq\exp(\frac{2\alpha+\beta}{\beta})\\ \end{align}
c_{max}\leq\exp(1+2\alpha/\beta)
c_{max}\leq \exp(1)
